{"tid":849902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「把男人當狗訓練可減少性虐」　假論文登上學術期刊","createTime":"2018-10-06T05:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T11:11:36.000Z","uid":81156,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad2f787b34a2f04d3bbc29fc790d80c626cc45e","tid":849902,"uid":81156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181006/640_e7d4b8957fd3b15700f8298683fb1a32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181006%2F640_e7d4b8957fd3b15700f8298683fb1a32.jpg&h=e413282e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「假論文」宣稱研究上萬隻狗狗的行為。<a href=\"http://翻攝Phys.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%BF%BB%E6%94%9DPhys.org&d=gp6lRm7seQHhmILTjdPMLEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=4ffc520f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">翻攝Phys.org</a>網站<br />\n<br />\n「狗公園是狗狗性侵的溫床」「把男人當做狗一樣的訓練，可以減少性侵案件」，「天文學本質就是性別歧視」，這些看來似是而非的論點，全出於三位學者刻意捏造的學術論文，他們發現，只要論文提及性別、種族或性行為等敏感議題，學術期刊的審查就沒有那麼嚴謹，胡謅一通也被當真，登上學術期刊。<br />\n<br />\n學術期刊的審核往往有漏洞，還可能有意識型態的偏見，3名美國的研究人員花了一年半時間，精心泡製20篇假論文，想要證實他們這個論點，儘管論文的結論超「瞎」，還是會唬到論文審核人員，結果竟有多達7篇假論文獲得刊登。<br />\n<br />\n其中一篇假論文名為「狗公園是狗狗性侵文化的溫床」，今年5月發表於《性別、地區與文化》期刊，論文宣稱研究者檢視過一萬隻狗狗的陰莖，文中指出，如果把男性當做狗一樣好好訓練，就能夠減少人類的性虐了。<br />\n<br />\n泡製假論文的學者之一是田納西大學數學博士林賽（James Lindsay），他說學術審稿委員通常以白人男性為主，只要看起來「政治正確」的新鮮話題，不管有多麼荒謬，他們都會當真。他和同伴寫假論文就是為了證明這一點。<br />\n<br />\n其中一篇假論文寫道，男性未經當事人同意，就一邊想著某位女性來自慰，應該可以當做是犯了性侵罪，另一篇假論文則是用比較新潮的語法改寫希特勒自傳《我的奮鬥》其中一個章節。林賽說，這顯示這些審稿的原則根本不值得信任。<br />\n<br />\n推特上不少網友拿這些論文搞笑，但也有學者表示，這顯示期刊審稿的內容應該更透明化。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）               <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181006/1442633/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181006%2F1442633%2F&d=gp6lRm7seQHhmILTjdPMLEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=1d21dc5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181006%2F1442633%2F&h=3ed226fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181006/1442633/</a>"},{"pid":"9bced3630d049f228d37cff6c15408cd38bf655f","tid":849902,"uid":58335,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:12:29.000Z","msg":"撚鳩D女權閪左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0392ac758ee249aeada9fd2fd7881d4b491cfb","tid":849902,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b60b9745c6f0d10eaf71ffe85a2a7a0a44234c0","tid":849902,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:20:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 啲期刊評審伏撚到仆街 投大陸台灣仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830965771ff6109a97436b24fbd0ff8fc4e1fd34","tid":849902,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"外國*"},{"pid":"102c57f20f873f3c57ae98d5e1177b97f58a60ab","tid":849902,"uid":135336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:20:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">男性未經當事人同意，就一邊想著某位女性來自慰，應該可以當做是犯了性侵罪</span></span> 屌你老母乜鳩都話係性侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22d4cb51e983537deefbc698d74414456af3a61","tid":849902,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:21:46.000Z","msg":"曲到圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d455326c8a23bf35f0b7c